{"tid":1605162,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【推到商台DJ見到】十一國殤朝早十點播願榮光","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:01:34.000Z","uid":85743,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"00993f5e5f2ad138e0563433a99f1c46bf515206","tid":1605162,"uid":85743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">10月1日 早上10:00<br />\n</span><br />\n國殤之日，大戰前夕，<br />\n以歌號召民眾，振奮人心，<br />\n祈求眾義士平安、武運亨通。<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》是我們的戰鬥曲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2A0Lao.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2A0Lao.png&h=cc9a9bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EfuMFJK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEfuMFJK.png&h=4ef5a210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n903好似比較可行，有潘小濤、森美<br />\n<br />\n如果商台願意播，我哋一定會扭開（好耐冇開的）收音機，大聲播，大聲唱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：中學之後好耐無聽電台，唔熟電台運作，唔可行由佢沈底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a115c78ed9e975cce04be8810227ec6d5d144c6b","tid":1605162,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"唔會啦，想俾人炒咩"},{"pid":"b3d2841ffd20070bf66133c3301855be50bd8311","tid":1605162,"uid":85743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a115c78ed9e975cce04be8810227ec6d5d144c6b","tid":1605162,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"唔會啦，想俾人炒咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:26:22.000Z","msg":"直接係Facebook tag潘小濤入嚟見我"},{"pid":"d782f3ae27b84023e9350a2453a1659c24d6efd6","tid":1605162,"uid":85743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">晴朗三子</span>"},{"pid":"b7bdd421ca315614d7361f4b4f3b255cc6382848","tid":1605162,"uid":85743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20